title: Tiffany Jackson, Texas Star Forward and W.N.B.A. Veteran, Dies at 37
description: She was an All-American in college and spent nine years as a pro. “I don’t think I’ve seen a player as competitive,” her college coach said.
dc:creator: Richard Sandomir
media:description: Tiffany Jackson in 2007, her final year on the University of Texas women’s basketball team. She was drafted by the New York Liberty that year with the fifth overall pick in the W.N.B.A. draft.
